---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us"
	description="Online casual games collection - Play anywhere, anytime"
>
	<div class="prose mx-auto py-8">
		<p class="text-lg  mb-6">
			Welcome to our online gaming paradise! Discover a rich collection of web-based games at your fingertips.
		</p>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<p>
				Our mission is to provide you with an enjoyable gaming experience. Whether you're waiting for the bus, 
				taking a lunch break, or just need a moment to relax, you can instantly access our games through your browser.
			</p>

			<p>
				We've carefully curated a variety of casual games, including:
			</p>
			
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
				<li>Puzzle & Brain Teasers</li>
				<li>Action & Adventure</li>
				<li>Strategy Games</li>
				<li>Casual Competition</li>
				<li>More is coming soon!</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				No downloads required - just open your browser and start playing! We regularly update our game collection
				to ensure there's always something new and exciting for you to enjoy.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
